Package edu.baylor.GroupFive.database.controllers

Class ReservationController

java.lang.Object
edu.baylor.GroupFive.database.controllers.ReservationController
public class ReservationController extends Object
This class represents a handler between our UI layer and our application layer. Methods from this class are called from our UI layer. ReservationController then determines which Service object in our application layer to continue operations with. The status of each operation is then returned to the UI layer.
Author:
Brendon, Icko, Chase, Cole
